                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Extend suit life by keeping neoprene supple and fresh while preventing fading, dryness, and premature aging; this 10 fl oz shampoo is good for 10 washes",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Treat stubborn urine or pet smells with Revivex Odor Eliminator, a natural formula that includes 20 washes (10 fl oz)",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "Wash off damaging salt crystals, chlorine, and organic residue from scuba equipment with Revivex B.C.D. Cleaner (10 fl oz) that’s good for 10 washes",
