        "product_description": {
            "value": "Keep your wetsuit fresh, clean, and long-lasting with this GEAR AID Wetsuit Cleaner and Conditioner kit. The concentrated shampoo gently removes salt, chlorine, and residue from neoprene after every dive, surf, or swim session, while the odor-fighting formula eliminates trapped smells to leave your gear smelling clean. Formulated to condition neoprene, it helps maintain flexibility and extend the life of your wetsuit and other neoprene gear. Simply add the concentrate to water, soak or rinse your wetsuit, and hang to dry. Ideal for surfers, divers, triathletes, and water sports enthusiasts who want to protect their investment and stay comfortable in the water.",
